headline: What You Need To Know Ahead of Linde’s Earnings Release
summary: Linde plc is expected to release its fiscal fourth-quarter earnings soon, and analysts project a modest earnings increase.

headline: Linde Announces Fourth Quarter 2025 Earnings and Conference Call Schedule
summary: WOKING, England, January 09, 2026--Linde (Nasdaq: LIN) will release its fourth quarter 2025 financial results by 06:00 EST/midday CET on Thursday, February 5, 2026. The Company will host and webcast its conference call at 09:00 EST/15:00 CET, which will be available to the public and the media in listen-only mode.
